#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 1. Cāpālavagga → pāvālavaggo (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn51.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Cāpālavagga"
msgstr "1. At the Cāpāla Shrine"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Apārasutta"
msgstr "1. From the Near Shore"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.254"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.1:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārome, bhikkhave, iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when these four bases of psychic power are developed and "
"cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore."

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy, "
"and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.5"
msgid "cittasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to mental "
"development, and active effort. "

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.6"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, "
"and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.1:1.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro iddhipādā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ "
"gamanāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When these four bases of psychic power are developed and cultivated they "
"lead to going from the near shore to the far shore.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.1:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
